	<para>
		This site is constructed with <application>Publican</application>, a free and open-source publishing tool developed by <ulink url="http://www.redhat.com/">Red Hat, Inc</ulink>. 
	</para>
	<para>
		<application>Publican</application> takes content authored in DocBook XML and transforms it into a variety of formats such as HTML, PDF, and EPUB. It can also build RPM packages to ship the content and can build documentation websites to publish the content on the web.
	</para>
	<para>
		<application>Publican</application> is included in the Fedora and Ubuntu distributions of Linux. Run <command>yum install publican</command> on Fedora or <command>apt-get install publican</command> on Ubuntu to install <application>Publican</application> on your system. An <ulink url="https://fedorahosted.org/releases/p/u/publican/">installer for Windows operating systems</ulink> is also available.
	</para>
